api_list.name: Update Email
Generate Email
api_list.description:
## Generate Email
This function will generate an email.
## Parameter Optional
**option (Array)**: ` [1,2,3,4,5,6]`
1 - Generate  public domain mail.
2 - Generate public Plus(+)  Gmail.
3- Generate  public Dot(.) Gmail.
4 - Generate private domain mail.
5 - Generate private Plus(+)  Gmail.
6- Generate  private Dot(.) Gmail.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://gmailnator.p.rapidapi.com/generate-email"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "gmailnator.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
